{"CHEW":[{"def":"To bite and grind with the teeth; to masticate.","pos":""},{"def":"To ruminate mentally; to meditate on.","pos":""}],"CHEWET":[{"def":"A kind of meat pie.","pos":""}],"CHEWINK":[{"def":"An american bird (Pipilo erythrophthalmus) of the Finch family, so called from its note; -- called also towhee bunting and ground robin.","pos":""}]}